Mail

===============
Got it 👍 — now you want a **real enterprise workflow**:

✔ Generate audit log
✔ Attach log file
✔ Send email automatically after playbook run

This is very common in enterprise automation (Ops / Audit / Compliance).

Below is the **clean enterprise way** using Ansible’s built-in `mail` module.

---

# 🧠 Enterprise Design (How it works)

After deployment finishes:

```
Generate Report
        ↓
Write Audit Log
        ↓
Send Email + Attach Log File
```

So we will add:

```
roles/
└── send_mail/   ⭐ NEW ROLE
```

---

# 🏗️ Updated Structure

```text
mstr-enterprise/
│
├── playbook.yml
├── vars/mstr_vars.yml
│
└── roles/
    ├── final_report/
    ├── send_mail/          ⭐ NEW
```

---

# ⭐ 1️⃣ Add Email Variables (IMPORTANT)

## `vars/mstr_vars.yml`

Add these values:

```yaml
# =========================
# EMAIL SETTINGS
# =========================

smtp_host: "smtp.company.com"
smtp_port: 25

mail_from: "mstr-automation@company.com"
mail_to: "platform-team@company.com"

mail_subject: "MSTR Deployment Audit Report"
```

(Your mail server team will provide SMTP host.)

---

# 🚀 2️⃣ Add Send Mail Role

## Folder

```text
roles/send_mail/tasks/main.yml
```

---

## ⭐ `roles/send_mail/tasks/main.yml`

```yaml
# =====================================================
# SEND AUDIT LOG VIA EMAIL
# =====================================================

- name: Send deployment audit log via email
  mail:
    host: "{{ smtp_host }}"
    port: "{{ smtp_port }}"
    from: "{{ mail_from }}"
    to: "{{ mail_to }}"
    subject: "{{ mail_subject }} - {{ overall_result }}"
    body: |
      Hello Team,

      MSTR deployment has completed.

      Overall Status : {{ overall_result }}
      Execution Time : {{ deploy_duration }} seconds

      Please find the attached audit log.

      Regards,
      MSTR Automation
    attach:
      - "{{ audit_log_file }}"
```

---

# ⭐ 3️⃣ Update Main Playbook (Final Step)

Add `send_mail` as the LAST role.

## `playbook.yml`

```yaml
roles:
  - ocp_login
  - prereq_check
  - istio_validation
  - cert_manager_validation
  - dependency_gate
  - cert_manager_install
  - mstr_operator_install
  - final_report
  - send_mail          # ⭐ LAST STEP
```

